Text.Page: Runekeepers are blocking the way to the {@Rgn:45003$$Vale of the Reaper}. If you can get through them and make contact with {@Rgn:45007$$Field Base Tenacity}, you'd be doing us a great service.
You're here from the {@Rgn:45002$$Tower Approach}? Good. I'm sure Rennie has something for you to do. That girl stays busy
Glad you got rid of some of those runekeepers. I hate those things.
